PHASE B — NEW SMART COUNT FLOWS (81–87)
========================================

Smart Count is accessed via the sparkle/AI icon visible within a storage's
item list (StorageDetailView). The three modes are Voice, Photo, and Sheet.

Navigation path to reach Smart Count:
  1. Sign in → Dashboard → tap any existing storage → storage detail opens
  2. Tap the AI/sparkle icon (accessibility id: "smart-count-button" or
     look for the icon next to the storage name in the toolbar)
  3. SmartCountView appears as a sheet showing three mode cards

If the button ID differs from the above, open AITest/Views/SmartCountView.swift
and AITest/Views/StorageDetailView.swift to find the actual accessibility
identifiers, then use those in the YAML.

